largement and compares the eu institutions and procedures to the political system of the united states us contact christophe crombez events & presentations workshop on public opinion institutions and representation in the european union april 7 2009 fsi stanford the europe center workshop christophe crombez karen long jusko joseph jupille simon hug fabio franchino cliff carrubba thomas konig jonathan rodden pdf+ conference agenda available search search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 9656 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
